title: Dalton rallies Bengals over Seahawks 27-24 in overtime
text:
> Washington Dalton rallies Bengals over Seahawks 27-24 in overtime Cincinnati Bengals quarterback Andy Dalton, center right, hugs offensive coordinator Hue Jackson after an NFL football game against the Seattle Seahawks, Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015, in Cincinnati. The Bengals won 27-24. (AP Photo/Gary Landers) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
